\c 16
\s Ukubusa kukaAhazi
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lesikhombisa kaPheka indodana kaRemaliya uAhazi indodana kaJothamu inkosi yakoJuda waba yinkosi.
\v 2 UAhazi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka elitshumi lesithupha eJerusalema. Kenzanga-ke okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe, njengoDavida uyise\x + 2 Lan. 28.1-4.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa wahamba ngendlela yamakhosi akoIsrayeli, yebo, futhi wenza indodana yakhe idabule emlilweni\x + Levi 18.21. Hlab. 106.37,38.\x*, njengezinengiso zezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazixotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 21.2. Dute. 12.31. 18.9.\x*.
\v 4 Wanikela imihlatshelo watshisa impepha endaweni eziphakemeyo\x + 14.4.\x* laphezu kwamaqaqa langaphansi kwaso sonke isihlahla esiluhlaza\x + 1 Kho. 14.23.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Khona uRezini inkosi yeSiriya loPheka indodana kaRemaliya, inkosi yakoIsrayeli, benyukela eJerusalema ukulwa, bamvimbezela uAhazi\x + Isa. 7.1,4-9.\x* kodwa kababanga lakho ukunqoba\x + 2 Lan. 28.5,6.\x*.
\v 6 Ngalesosikhathi uRezini inkosi yeSiriya wabuyisela iElathi eSiriya, waxotsha amaJuda eElathi; amaSiriya asesiza eElathi ahlala khona kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 7 UAhazi wasethuma izithunywa kuTigilathi Pileseri inkosi yeAsiriya esithi: Ngiyinceku yakho lendodana yakho; yenyuka ungisindise esandleni senkosi yeSiriya lesandleni senkosi yakoIsrayeli abangivukelayo\x + 2 Lan. 28.16,20,21.\x*.
\v 8 UAhazi\x + 2 Lan. 28.16,20,21.\x* wasethatha isiliva legolide okwakutholwa endlini kaJehova lenothweni yendlu yenkosi\x + 12.18.\x*, wathumela isipho enkosini yeAsiriya\x + 1 Kho. 15.19.\x*.
\v 9 Inkosi yeAsiriya yasimlalela, ngoba inkosi yeAsiriya yenyuka imelene leDamaseko yayithumba, ya\add ba\add*thumbela eKiri \add abantu ba\add*yo, yabulala uRezini\x + Isa. 22.6. Amos 1.5. 9.7.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Inkosi uAhazi yasisiya eDamaseko ukuhlangana loTigilathi Pileseri inkosi yeAsiriya, yabona ilathi elaliseDamaseko. Inkosi uAhazi yasithumela kuUriya umpristi\x + Isa. 8.2.\x* isimo selathi lomfanekiso walo njengokwenziwa kwalo konke.
\v 11 U-Uriya umpristi wasesakha ilathi njengakho konke uAhazi akuthumela kuvela eDamaseko; uUriya umpristi wenza njalo, yaze yafika inkosi uAhazi ivela eDamaseko.
\v 12 Inkosi isibuyile eDamaseko inkosi yalibona ilathi. Inkosi yasondela elathini, yanikela phezu kwalo\x + 2 Lan. 26.16,18,19.\x*.
\v 13 Yasitshisa umnikelo wayo wokutshiswa lomnikelo wayo wokudla, yathela umnikelo wayo wokunathwayo, yafafaza igazi leminikelo yokuthula eyayilayo phezu kwelathi.
\v 14 Kodwa ilathi lethusi elaliphambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 2 Lan. 4.1.\x*\nd* yaliletha lisuka phambi kwendlu\x + Eks. 40.6,29.\x*, lisuka phakathi kwelathi lendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 16.11.\x*\nd*, yalifaka ehlangothini lwenyakatho lwelathi\x + 16.11.\x*.
\v 15 Inkosi uAhazi yasimlaya uUriya umpristi isithi: Phezu kwelathi elikhulu\x + 16.11.\x* tshisa umnikelo wokutshiswa wekuseni, lomnikelo wokudla wantambama, lomnikelo wokutshiswa wenkosi, lomnikelo wayo wokudla, lomnikelo wokutshiswa wabo bonke abantu belizwe, lomnikelo wabo wokudla, leminikelo yabo yokunathwayo; ufafaze phezu kwalo lonke igazi lomnikelo wokutshiswa lalo lonke igazi lomhlatshelo\x + Eks. 29.39,40,41.\x*. Kodwa ilathi lethusi lizakuba ngelami ukubuza \add ngalo\x + 2 Lan. 4.1.\x*\add*.
\v 16 U-Uriya umpristi wasesenza njengakho konke inkosi uAhazi eyayikulayile.
\p
\v 17 Inkosi uAhazi yasiquma\x + 24.13. 2 Lan. 28.24.\x* imiphetho yezisekelo, yasusa inditshi yokugezela kuzo\x + 1 Kho. 7.27,28,38.\x*, yethula ulwandle phezu kwenkabi zethusi ezazingaphansi kwalo\x + 1 Kho. 7.23,25.\x*, yalubeka phezu kokugandelwe ngamatshe.
\v 18 Lokwembesiweyo kwesabatha ababekwakhe endlini, lentuba yenkosi phandle, yakususa endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngenxa yenkosi yeAsiriya.
\p
\v 19 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAhazi azenzayo, kazibhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 28.26,27.\x*?
\v 20 UAhazi waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa kuboyise emzini kaDavida. UHezekhiya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 28.27.\x*.